citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3:36 pm on 17-JUN-
2022. Went to the venue on the itinerary in Puyallup, WA; however, I did not see the licensee. I then called the contact
number and was able to speak with him. The licensee stated he had been delayed in traffic and was still in Oregon.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3:36 pm on 17-JUN-
2022.  Went to the venue on the itinerary in Puyallup, WA; however, I did not see the licensee.  I then called the contact 
number and was able to speak with him.  The licensee stated he had been delayed in traffic and was still in Oregon. 
 
 
 
End Section
